ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"中槍男子須再接受手術 被燒傷男子3成皮膚燒傷<br />\n<br />\n昨日西灣河衝突中中槍受傷的21歲男子，目前情況仍然危殆，消息指，佢腹部中槍，要接受肝臟和腎臟手術，現時仍在東區醫院深切治療部留醫。至於昨天在馬鞍山懷疑被人淋易燃液體後點火燒傷的57歲男子，據了解他有3成皮膚二級燒傷，目前仍在沙田威爾斯醫院深切治療部留醫。昨日多區發生衝突，共128人受傷送院，除兩名危殆男子外，另外4人情況嚴重，63人情況穩定，58人已出院，尚有1人暫時未確定情況。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-12 11:22:41"},{"pid":"7bfd85e60556895d8a97be3e21b35125ceed003e","tid":1709462,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>黑警死全家</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf07900751d407054eb2bf904c6498be264811e9","tid":1709462,"uid":125935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"中環LUNCH TIME<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b3a6b7df229b6f552ae1791e3896f619423643","tid":1709462,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"中大要人要物資！情況好危！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1709927\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1709927</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n暴大告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e503898208972958dde33e1c77d37b728966cc2c","tid":1709462,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"港式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c092a9a399ba3f2626ee105a15dbf8219af54238","tid":1709462,"uid":7778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T06:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJ4GhPU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi